    <developer_name>Torrey Sorensen</developer_name>
    <summary>A Game System for making games and programs in Groovy. (A Fantasy Console idea)</summary>
    
    <description>
        <p>Leikr Game System</p>
	<p>Use the editors you are most comfortable with to create games or programs in Groovy code, maps in Tiled the popular map editor, make sprites using a simple single png file. See the github wiki for more help and tutorials.</p>
        <p>The word Leikr is Old Norse for Game and is a play on the name Lego, from the Danish “Leg Godt”, meaning “Play Well”.</p>
	<p>Press ESC to exit the system.</p>
    </description>
